8 Statement of purpose of bill as introduced: This bill proposes to authorize the
9 use of Class B(2) waters in the State for use by a hydroelectric power
10 generation facility with a proposed installed capacity of five megawatts or less.
11 The bill would also direct the Secretary of Natural Resources to amend the
12 Vermont Water Quality Standards to reflect the inclusion of hydroelectric
13 power generation facilities with a proposed installed capacity of five
14 megawatts or less as a suitable use of Class B(2) waters.
15 An act relating to authorizing the use of State waters by hydroelectric
16 generation facilities
